    <title>Program 7 - CSS Box Model</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .box {
            width: 300px;
            background-color: lightblue;

            /* Box Model Properties */
            border: 5px solid black;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>CSS Box Model Example</h1>

    <div class="box">
        This box demonstrates the CSS Box Model.
        <br><br>
        It includes margin, border, padding and content.
    </div>

    <p>
        The space outside the border is margin,
        the space between border and content is padding.
    </p>

